          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="references" class="doc-section-title">References</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Design tokens and resources for implementing the Page Header component.</p>
            <ul class="doc-list">
              <li><strong>Figma Node:</strong> <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">17220:1199408</code> &#8212; Component Set: Page Header</li>
              <li><strong>Total Variants:</strong> 4 Structure values (Default, With Summary, With Tabs, Full)</li>
              <li><strong>Typography:</strong> Zoho Puvi Semibold (600) for title, Medium (500) for breadcrumb / tabs / buttons</li>
              <li><strong>Component Width:</strong> <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">960 px</code> (full-width layout)</li>
            </ul>
